{"tid":1993323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日出康城36歲女子上吊　丈夫發現報警惜太遲","createTime":"2020-04-28T16:32:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T16:59:55.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"70cd6d27d2e9f811e6a2d3493ab354b88a371990","tid":1993323,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T16:32:43.000Z","msg":"今日（28日）下午2時許，將軍澳日出康城1名男子報案 ，指其36歲姓郭妻子在洗手間內以晾衣繩上吊，家傭發現並將她解下。救護員接報到場，將昏迷女事主送往將軍澳醫院搶救，惟其後證實不治。警方於現場沒有檢獲遺書，初步調查相信事件沒有可疑，女事主死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：黃廸雯"},{"pid":"40b36fce524d8d00fb07478b2d4f6f50e630fbf2","tid":1993323,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T16:38:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1kJ7Ufw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1kJ7Ufw.gif&h=ee5bd90a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新登記選民截止日期：2020年5月2日</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk2020.vote/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk2020.vote%2F&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImFYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=54e2283d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk2020.vote/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jL0uupX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjL0uupX.gif&h=b8ede5bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><code>圖片來源：#35432 速食保濟丸 @LIHKG</code><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1990059\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1990059</a></div><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xmNHPoS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxmNHPoS.gif&h=f83b829f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FWbUF5p.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFWbUF5p.gif&h=673c58e5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d2721591fa47cefaf1923a5d5ae61c82b12984e0","tid":1993323,"uid":83907,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T16